Article 3-2 (Master Plans on Erosion Control Work)
* The Minister of Korea Forest Service shall formulate and implement a master plan on erosion control
* Basic objectives of and direction for the erosion control work;
* Matters necessary to facilitate the development of erosion control technology and the utilization
* Matters concerning regions subject to erosion control work and post-management thereof;
* Matters concerning the nurturing of technical human resources for erosion control work;
* Matters concerning the expansion of international exchanges of erosion control technology;
* Other matters deemed necessary by the Minister of Korea Forest Service.
* A master plan may be amended where there are extenuating grounds for modification regarding
